    {489,"Warsong Gulch",0,"A valley Bordering Ashenvale Forest and the Barrens, Warsong Gulch hosts a constant battle between the Horde and Alliance.\n\n\n\nAs a 10 vs 10 capture-the-flag battleground, the first faction to capture three flags is victorious.\n\n\n\nEager to aid their allies, members of every race in Azeroth rush to the Gulch to lend sword, or spell, to the conflict.",{"wago"},3277,"PVPZone03",3,122,1,-1},
